Source: hand-written by Rigor maintainers (no upstream RBS available
        in `ruby/gem_rbs_collection` as of 2026-05-15).
Reference: PostgreSQL `pg` gem README + libpq documentation.
License: MPL-2.0 (matches the rest of Rigor).

This stub covers the `PG.connect` / `PG::Connection` / `PG::Result`
surface that real-world Rails projects actually call (Mastodon,
GitLab FOSS, OpenProject, Diaspora, etc.). The full libpq surface
is intentionally not covered. PRs to extend the coverage are
welcome.
